headline: HavocAI Adds $85M in New Capital to Scale Proven Autonomy Capabilities
summary: HavocAI, a leading developer of maritime autonomous systems, today announced it has secured $85 million in new capital. The funding comes from new investors B Capital, In-Q-Tel, Lockheed Martin, Hanwha, Taiwania, Vanderbilt University, Up Partners, Island Green Capital, and Zero Infinity Partners, along with continued support from Scout Ventures and Outlander Ventures in addition to other early funders.
